<list>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

 Data Access: Web data (e.g., <link>
HTML tables</link>, <format wordnetid="106636806" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../489/93489.xml">
RSS</link></format>
 feeds, <format wordnetid="106636806" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../906/501906.xml">
CSV</link></format>
 files), external databases (e.g., <system wordnetid="104377057" confidence="0.8">
<artifact wordnetid="100021939" confidence="0.8">
<instrumentality wordnetid="103575240" confidence="0.8">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../545/19545.xml">
MySQL</link></instrumentality>
</artifact>
</system>
, <company wordnetid="108058098" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../591/22591.xml">
Oracle</link></company>
) and local data files (e.g., <software wordnetid="106566077" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<format wordnetid="106636806" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../268/20268.xml">
Excel</link></format>
</software>
, <software wordnetid="106566077" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../935/20935.xml">
Access</link></software>
, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../109/1116109.xml">
text-delimited data</link>).</entry>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

 Data Analysis: Sorts, filters, copies, queries, calculated fields and relationships.</entry>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

 Reporting</entry>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

 Scripting and Extensions: Data-enabled version of <programming_language wordnetid="106898352" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../845/9845.xml">
JavaScript</link></programming_language>
 with support for <programming_language wordnetid="106898352" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../004/29004.xml">
SQL</link></programming_language>
.</entry>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

 Other: Runs on Microsoft Windows NT/2000/XP/Vista and <O wordnetid="106832680" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../298/990298.xml">
Ubuntu</link></O>
 Linux; supports up to 18 <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../756/9756.xml">
exabytes</link> per project; 60 billion records per table; 250 million table per project.</entry>
